{"tid":1810401,"cid":23,"subCid":0,"title":"[大家要將畫面拉闊一點] 買咗部xpan","createTime":"2020-01-04T00:03:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-11T16:11:36.000Z","uid":133377,"like":59,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"a94922356a7698436f7a8f4f61d8b4cdb2976721","tid":1810401,"uid":133377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T00:03:29.000Z","msg":"今次破例聽江sir鳩up<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/moBH8k2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmoBH8k2.jpg&h=95331cb1&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n那怕外面由一萬炒到兩萬幾，逃走唔係一個選擇<br />\nerr..不過一卷菲林36變成19張，曬相仲要加錢真係好痛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋部機真係有啲重<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UpXTvBp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUpXTvBp.jpg&h=1991a036&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kEnoSPN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkEnoSPN.jpg&h=28d053ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n第一日出去試機，個人覺得實際畫面闊過取景器，同埋會偏低小小，裂像對焦真係唔夠leica好，個對比度真係比較低，配90mm仲難用，對我呢個盲毛嚟講簡直災難，今次用既菲林係最後一批既agfavista 200..唉好似乜Q菲林都停曬產咁<br />\n<br />\n跟住去咗個旅行，啱啱彩圖麗晨早六點send咗相過嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />呢次用既係富士C200，天皇賣緊過期個批，用落都ok<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EsH0U24.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEsH0U24.jpg&h=d7e24fc3&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3bQxL9L.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3bQxL9L.jpg&h=77bf5972&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n似乎都係要買翻個中灰filter..但係xpan配件都係超貴，原裝hood呀，近視屈光鏡片呀..全部夠膽賣1500以上<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0Kcwhgr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0Kcwhgr.jpg&h=38be19e8&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\nf/4感覺成日唔係好夠用，上面呢張震咗，但係壓細咗之後睇落勉強ok<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/84Q56g7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F84Q56g7.jpg&h=26f5dca8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仲有一卷黑白沖緊，遲啲再同大家分享吓，呢度有冇其他xpan用家一齊討論吓貼吓相？<br />\n<br />\n另外作為菲林新手其實仲係唔識點樣可以運用底片優勢，例如影谷沖keep住快門速度。想問吓有冇巴打可以指教吓？比如如果我影到一半到夜晚，我可唔可以部分影under谷沖？上網睇過唔係好明<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28f9fbdc4a8adaa679176288c4ec76b7cdb63bee","tid":1810401,"uid":185452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T01:14:47.000Z","msg":"應該冇得部分谷。<br />\n<br />\n詳細不如直接打電話俾 彩圖麗 問問？"},{"pid":"923cd4973ee178a8bc506f324b70bede71234526","tid":1810401,"uid":120865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T02:08:46.000Z","msg":"好有米 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d617d2f6ccacdaaa483477fd1046a36ebb0124bf","tid":1810401,"uid":14535,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"923cd4973ee178a8bc506f324b70bede71234526","tid":1810401,"uid":120865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T02:08:46.000Z","msg":"好有米 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T03:19:52.000Z","msg":"樓豬不嬲都係有錢仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好似係"},{"pid":"214ad320960dc382ce0eef2ee2d347d55dbdd8a3","tid":1810401,"uid":14535,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"28f9fbdc4a8adaa679176288c4ec76b7cdb63bee","tid":1810401,"uid":185452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T01:14:47.000Z","msg":"應該冇得部分谷。<br />\n<br />\n詳細不如直接打電話俾 彩圖麗 問問？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T03:21:18.000Z","msg":"換菲林可以解決問題<br />\n不過電子機有好多會回哂 要帶抽申器係身 好麻煩"},{"pid":"504ff13dbe44ebe9ad5e3774ce4e3fe495933249","tid":1810401,"uid":14